snippet.title: Be Kind To Yourself — Nice Things People Said Trailer — Now also on Itch.io
snippet.description:
BKTY is an arcade puzzle game and people seem to like it!

Get it from
Playdate Catalog — https://play.date/games/be-kind-to-yourself/
Itch.io — https://mouflon-cloud.itch.io/be-kind-to-yourself

Music in trailer and in the game is by Seth Walker: https://soundcloud.com/sethamakessounds
https://freesound.org/people/Seth_Makes_Sounds/
